{"tid":1697904,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"死人花牌伍黑心 - 陳也","createTime":"2019-11-07T06:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T09:02:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd83d44734aa7608dfbf802624a15c75883bfe2c","tid":1697904,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:42:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191107/20801279/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191107%2F20801279%2F&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNVKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=da054e91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191107%2F20801279%2F&h=a5831b98\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191107/20801279/</a><br />\n<br />\n死人花牌伍黑心 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191107/large/1573032557_f5f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191107%2Flarge%2F1573032557_f5f7.jpg&h=9ad7b7ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港電台新聞截圖(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n韓正有什麼肺話交托林奠？為她臨終前奠定禍港之母終極冠名？唔使了，呢塊死人花牌，早就寫好，壽終正寢，千古不義。<br />\n<br />\n要她再做更多嗱渣嘢嗎？五個月下來，嗱喳招循環又循環，社工又試被當面噴椒兼逮捕，記者被拉黑警以為講一千次「假記者」就會成真。咁樣係唔會令傳媒工作者驚嘅。而年輕救護員中了加料TG，成個背脊「花晒」那張照片，外國朋友冇聽清楚就問：伊拉克拍嘅？唔係？智利嗎？聽到是香港，與香港人同樣中意行mall的她黯然失語。科大生為避TG墮樓重創，做競選簡介集會的區議員被黑警「教訓」未拉票已經被拉，太古城西區議員趙家賢在商場被咬甩耳朵，行兇者先刀插途人，擺明做血腥騷「交數」。種種暴行，似曾相識，韓正落林奠柯打，林奠叫二哥執生，後者拍心口搵黑社會換過件衫使命easy必達。重複的爆缸，想令身心受創的香港人疲乏而萌生退場灰念。可是，三千個被捕者跨年齡界別、他們的親屬、師友們最低門檻都牽涉三四十萬人，香港人，無可能割肉割席。雖然運動反覆受挫，若然我們放棄，淪為與「伍黑心」一樣的死人花牌，靈堂俾個位置你擺，有柒用咩。 <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"3219bea86eaeb51247a3eabbf58db18e71e94c27","tid":1697904,"uid":313198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T06:54:47.000Z","msg":"想放棄想輸，入嚟聽完首歌再決定<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697147\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697147</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"924176ed277c043244670fb5e08fc6b8504b56a1","tid":1697904,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T08:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b298d413d1b9d77166f0ccb142a91d0353e6d50","tid":1697904,"uid":182192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T09:02:07.000Z","msg":"不屈進行曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}